  "keyFeatures": [
    "Static type checking with optional type annotations",
    "Type inference to reduce annotation boilerplate",
    "Generics for reusable, type-safe code",
    "Structural type system (duck typing)",
    "Interfaces and type aliases for describing shapes",
    "Enums for named constant sets",
    "Decorators for metaprogramming",
    "JSX support for React and other frameworks",
    "Module and namespace support",
    "Incremental compilation for large projects",
    "Watch mode for continuous compilation",
    "Project references for monorepo setups",
    "Language Server Protocol (tsserver) for IDE integration",
    "Declaration file generation (.d.ts)",
    "Source map support for debugging"
